#### ExcelParserService

**Location:** `com.hireright.sourceintelligence.service.impl.ExcelParserService`

**Purpose:** Parse Excel files and extract institution records.

**Responsibilities:**
1. Read Excel files (.xlsx and .xls formats)
2. Extract data from cells and convert to `InstitutionRecord` objects
3. Handle various cell types (String, Numeric, Boolean, Formula, Blank)
