- `isRowEmpty()` - Checks if row contains data

**Excel File Structure Expected:**

| Column | Field | Description |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| 0 | Institution Name | Name of the institution |
| 1 | Country | Country location |
| 2 | City | City location |
| 3 | State/County/Region | State or region |
| 4 | Service Provider | Vendor service provider |
| 5 | Surcharge Amount | Additional charges |
