### 7. Error Recovery Strategies

#### Partial Success Handling
- Process continues even if some records fail
- Track failed/not found records
- Return comprehensive statistics
- Client can retry failed records

#### Transaction Management
- Use `@Transactional` for atomicity
- Rollback on exceptions within processor
- Each record processed independently
- Prevents partial updates to single record

#### Graceful Degradation
- Return partial results when possible
- Include error details in response
- Don't fail entire batch for single record
- Provide actionable feedback

