#### SQL/NoSQL Injection Protection

**Parameterized Queries:**
- MongoDB queries use parameterized criteria
- `Pattern.quote()` escapes special regex characters
- Prevents regex injection attacks

**Spring Data MongoDB:**
- Uses parameterized queries by default
- Prevents NoSQL injection
- Type-safe query building

